data.description: Welcome to 103 San Marcos Dr. this home is truly better then new! It has been exquisitely maintained with neutral colors throughout. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 baths including 2 on suites. The spacious home office makes the perfect place to work or create a media room/ playroom. The fabulous kitchen is open to a large living room with a beautiful fireplace and soaring ceilings. The gem of this property is the almost HALF ACRE LOT!! Snatch up your opportunity get a great home and lot and a fantastic price!
